Reinitialization will only involve non-interface related configuration settings. The baud rate will stay at the current Service Port Mode setting

test.doc: Verify that replies of Service port mode work correctly when sending the $ [Message] for every different format messages. The $ message has the following format: $<Application Command>[,<Application Command>]<CR> Where $ is an ASCII character with the value of 0x24 <CR> is an ASCII character with the value of 0x0D <Application Command> include 2 part: [Command][Data] 1. [Command] field contains composed of printable ASCII characters in the range of 0x30 (‘0’) to 0x7A (‘z’). 2. [Data] field contains values represented by ASCII Hex characters.
